AbstractUIWithFields_mxJPO
 class AbstractUIWithFields_mxJPO.Field

Class used to define a column of a web table or a field of a web form.

Method Detail

parse

void parse(String _url,
           String _content)
Parses a field / column. This includes:
  • alt label
  • HRef href
  • range HRef in rangeHref
  • label
  • name
  • sortType
  • expression
  • isBusinessObject or isRelationship expression
  • users who have access to a field / column
  • settings

Parameters:
_url - URL to parse
_content - content of the URL to parse
